text:
It's about things that
caught my attention during work!

Oh, really?
Like what happened today? What did you write about?

I wrote about the costumes that all
of 283PRO will wear... And also about the future!

The future?
Like your future dreams?

Yes!
Things I want to do while wearing the costumes!

Like concerts, events,
and various things!

I see, that sounds great!
I might try writing down things I want to do too.

Haha, you caught me.
Let's grab something to eat first!
